     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>程序主要是通过</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Spring</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>容器来访问容器中的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>&lt;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Bean</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>&gt;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ApplicationContext</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>是</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Spring</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>容器最常用的接口，该接口有如下两个实现类：</span></li>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ClassPathXmlApplicationContext</span><span

     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>常用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>)</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>从类加载路径下搜索配置文件，并根据配置文件来创建</span><span

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>

     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>FileSystemXmlApplicationContext</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-size:12.0pt'><span

style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Spring</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>容器</span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";color:#333333'>。</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#333333'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>容器对象</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>(</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ApplicationContext</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>)</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>创建时，读取配置文件，

  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  vertical-align:top;width:6.1409in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>显式地关闭应用程序上下文的方式。当调用</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>close()</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>方法时，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Spring</span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>将销毁应用程序上下文中的所有</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>bean</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>，并释放所有相关的资源。在这种情况下，</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Spring</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>不会等待</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>JVM</span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>关闭钩子触发，而是立即关闭应用程序上下文。</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:2.1027in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt'>registerShutdownHook()</p>
  </td>
  <td style='border-style:solid;border-color:#A3A3A3;border-width:1pt;
  background-color:#E7E6E6;vertical-align:top;width:6.1409in;padding:2.0pt 3.0pt 2.0pt 3.0pt'>
  <p style='font-size:11.5pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>一种注册</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>JVM</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>关闭钩子的方式。当</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>JVM</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>关闭时，</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>JVM</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>关闭钩子会被触发，并自动关闭应用程序上下文。在这种情况下，</span><span
  style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Spring</span><span style='font-family:
  "Microsoft YaHei UI"'>会等待</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>JVM</span><span
  style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>关闭钩子触发，并在触发时关闭应用程序上下文。</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

</div>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>通常情况下，建议使用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>
     registerShutdownHook() </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>方法来关闭应用程序上下文，因为这样可以确保在</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> JVM </span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>关闭时正确地关闭应用程序上下文。但是，在某些情况下，可能需要使用</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> close() </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>方法来显式地关闭应用程序上下文。例如，在某些</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Web </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>应用程序中，可能需要在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> Web </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>容器关闭之前显式地关闭应用程序上下文。</span></li>
</ul>
